{"tid":858813,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"百里香遊記","createTime":"2018-10-12T05:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T12:22:23.000Z","uid":60470,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"55c66cd148079c6fe8d6bf8db858665991280343","tid":858813,"uid":60470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:20:44.000Z","msg":"上晝做完野途經觀塘，特登去試下呢期好紅既百里香餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未夠12點去到仲有大把位，但坐落無耐就多人過翻印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n皇牌燒雞調味有誠意，唔係一味死咸，香草味有層次，唔錯，唯獨雞胸位都係比較鞋口乾身<br />\n薯角就都係果啲貨，比M記咸啲，勝在新鮮量多，食哂我覺得都幾飽<br />\n包凍檸茶45算係咁，值得一試，不過又唔至於要特登再過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n（題外話：究竟隔離靚仔巴打係點用一隻叉食到成碟雞乾乾淨淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/12/131852_4fdd01c2ad6650c71477879cc4c745ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F131852_4fdd01c2ad6650c71477879cc4c745ab.png&h=c244be6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/12/131854_c021bb63c763f5b27aad8e38a1a8ef20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F131854_c021bb63c763f5b27aad8e38a1a8ef20.png&h=ed865144&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc7eca45803484bae0dbdd4fe43b7df16e60d8ea","tid":858813,"uid":25028,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:22:26.000Z","msg":"見到隻雞d色就知邊d係打手邊d係真食客"},{"pid":"ee19952085d56fbf3599af5d47948217d0d48250","tid":858813,"uid":18129,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:23:06.000Z","msg":"靚仔圖呢？"},{"pid":"6e791ececd01814af53f3a82880c4e48b107f4cd","tid":858813,"uid":113064,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:23:21.000Z","msg":"一剔過<br />\nA、B、C、D餐係固定午餐<br />\n而E、F、G、H餐係每星期都轉一次<br />\n連埋蒜包餐湯凍飲 原價$45 / 48 / 50蚊<br />\n1230前埋單 / 1415後入坐減5蚊<br />\n盛惠$40 / 43 / 45蚊<br />\n推介菜式係皇牌燒雞 + 避風塘脆薯皇<br />\n星期六會送埋甜品 暫時係焦糖燉蛋<br />\n<br />\n百里香 觀塘駿業街67號熟食市場1樓44號<br />\n路線：港鐵觀塘站A2出口 步行約6分鐘<br />\n營業時間：一至五11:00-16:30；六11:00-16:00<br />\n外賣熱線：67082851<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">資料由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原創者</span>那吾克儉提供</span>"},{"pid":"fcce7c5024ed00a4f770202de389d13ea6487628","tid":858813,"uid":2660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc7eca45803484bae0dbdd4fe43b7df16e60d8ea","tid":858813,"uid":25028,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:22:26.000Z","msg":"見到隻雞d色就知邊d係打手邊d係真食客"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:23:34.000Z","msg":"我真食客"},{"pid":"098f3de491686e72eca37024d23c840daada2202","tid":858813,"uid":33359,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:23:58.000Z","msg":"值得一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b551d959f38e3f8390f74cfa1524d21f243fa0","tid":858813,"uid":113064,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:24:44.000Z","msg":"想問下印度佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢篇食評攞到幾多人工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3073b386f683abbaa02dd1b600c40f080589231a","tid":858813,"uid":60470,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"bc7eca45803484bae0dbdd4fe43b7df16e60d8ea","tid":858813,"uid":25028,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:22:26.000Z","msg":"見到隻雞d色就知邊d係打手邊d係真食客"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:25:00.000Z","msg":"所有相親自拍攝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純天然無P圖"},{"pid":"91982c9c60b1989403d650235d197e6a982779ba","tid":858813,"uid":60470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee19952085d56fbf3599af5d47948217d0d48250","tid":858813,"uid":18129,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:23:06.000Z","msg":"靚仔圖呢？"